spec_data.Name: yum-plugin-priorities
spec_data.Description:
This plugin allows repositories to have different priorities.
Packages in a repository with a lower priority can't be overridden by packages
from a repository with a higher priority even if repo has a later version.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 09:02:53 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: plugin to give priorities to packages from different repos
